Package: roughnote
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-4-1, libc6, libcairo2
Maintainer: https://github.com/kamallearner123/ClassBoard
Description: A native Linux drawing and note-taking application
 A native Linux drawing and comprehensive note-taking application built
 with Rust and GTK4.
 .
 To build and install from source on Debian/Ubuntu:
   $ sudo apt update
   $ sudo apt install -y cargo git libgtk-4-dev pkg-config
   $ cargo build --release --locked
   $ sudo install -Dm755 target/release/roughnote /usr/bin/roughnote
